rComments: I would take it again! She is GRRRRREAT!  p.s. Assigned readings (PDF files), no textbook

I love this class! It's a very easy class if you pay attention and read the powerpoints that are posted. Most of the assignments and exams are analyzing art at a critical level and not a lot of theory needs to be memorized to pass with flying colours. I'll be taking her class again for sure!
